{"tid":1501262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[黨鐵幫兇］聽晚八點去屋企附近既地鐵站查詢","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T18:48:11.000Z","uid":27203,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0559e1f93c68a7d0ab94ba44183d488cf0fd4b","tid":1501262,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:01.000Z","msg":"一個站你就關到 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全部地鐵都有居民落黎查詢又點</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係要癱瘓地鐵/阻礙列車行駛<br />\n<br />\n我地淨係想港鐵交代呢一啲問題：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 係唔係配合警方所有指示 罔顧所有市民利益？<br />\n2. 關咩站至咩站有咩準則？時間幾耐你話事？<br />\n3. 若果市民因鐵路關閉而出左任何事顧 係咪港鐵負責？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非查詢 唔好破壞<br />\n人數係最大優勢<br />\n我地唔去前線都要保護勇武 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武手足荃葵青後休息 辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"071962f3cc06c67576dbb382353eb83f5fef1714","tid":1501262,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"652ab3aaacbc41ff81ff48aa479c77f3f5509862","tid":1501262,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:28.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"c4c846b56727e2a3ef9e1c70808010ea1bc38f56","tid":1501262,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"6c3300731a51c3141bccf00e85c2fe0234c6b710","tid":1501262,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:48.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"41c4c4df069425ba1f479869a077fd575ffc348e","tid":1501262,"uid":27203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:1